Package: ReactomeGraph4R
Title: R Interface for the Reactome Graph Database
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Chi-Lam", "Poon", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "clpoon807@gmail.com", 
            comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6298-7099")),
    person("Reactome", role = "cph", email = "help@reactome.org"))
Description: Pathways, reactions, and biological entities in Reactome knowledge 
    are systematically represented as an ordered network and stored in the Reactome 
    Graph Database. This package is provides an interface to query interconnected 
    datain the Reactome Graph Database. There is also another package, 
    ReactomeContentService4R, for queries in the Content Service.
